o Guduric, Vanja Marinkovic, Ognjen Dobric, Filip Petrusev, Nikola Milutinov, Dusan Ristic, Aleksa Avramovic, Ognjen Jaramaz, Dejan Davidovac, and Uros Plavsic will compete for the remaining eight roster spots.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filip_Petru\\u0161ev\", \"score\": 0.9999999262890951, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filip Petrusev\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filip_Petru\\u0161ev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filip_Petru\\u0161ev\"}, {\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Milutinov\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikola Milutinov\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Milutinov\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Milutinov\"}, {\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du\\u0161an_Risti\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999934739208, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dusan Ristic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du\\u0161an_Risti\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du\\u0161an_Risti\\u0107\"}, {\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleksa_\\u0110ura\\u0161evi\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.454999991887014, \"rank\": 0.8131868131867451, \"text\": \"Aleksa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleksa_\\u0110ura\\u0161evi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleksa_\\u0110ura\\u0161evi\\u0107\"}, {\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dejan_Davidovac\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dejan Davidovac\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"